:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 503114007: Config/Level/Mission/5031140/Act/Act503114007.json-->
:'''Sunday:''' May I help you, {{MC|f=ma'am|m=sir}}?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
:{{DIcon}} Just wanted to chat with you, Sunny.
::'''Sunday:''' ...I'll tell you everything I know, but I'd prefer not to be called that in the future.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503114008_16-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503114008_16-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Life on the Express...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115104-->
:::'''Sunday:''' Please ask away. But I might not have a lot to share since I've only recently came on board.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503114008_19-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503114008_19-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the companions on the Express...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115106-->
::::'''Sunday:''' I'm trying to connect with everyone using my new identity, but I may need some time due to my personality.
::::'''Sunday:''' Mr. Yang showed me the captivating way of the Trailblaze during our travels. Truth be told, you've all been great teachers.
::::'''Sunday:''' The conductor taught me about the history of the Nameless, Dan Heng showed me the extensive knowledge stored in the data bank, and even from Miss March 7th, I've learned...
::::'''Sunday:''' ...
::::'''Sunday:''' A lot.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} About your book...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115112-->
::::'''Sunday:''' It was a gift I received, and it arrived blank.
::::'''Sunday:''' Did you mistake it for some type of classic text or something? It's not entirely inaccurate, though. I wrote some pages myself.
::::'''Sunday:''' In a way, it symbolizes a chapter of my life.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} What have you been up to lately?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115116-->
::::'''Sunday:''' Most of the time, I've been reflecting in solitude while waiting for our departure.
::::'''Sunday:''' I wanted to contribute, but I wasn't sure how. The conductor just told me to wait patiently.
::::'''Sunday:''' Yet... as I look at the spacious car, I feel a strong urge to organize it that likely stems from boredom...
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Return}} Talk about something else...
::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503114008_16-->
:::;(<!--Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString)-->)
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About Sunday...
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115121-->
:::::'''Sunday:''' My past isn't worth mentioning. But may I ask what piqued your curiosity?
:::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503114008_38-->
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503114008_38-->
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About The Family...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115123-->
::::::'''Sunday:''' The Planet of Festivities is certainly well-known, but among The Family's many territories, it is merely a "hotel" at best.
::::::'''Sunday:''' Perhaps we'll visit more domains of the Harmony someday. I'll make sure to excuse myself to avoid any complications.
::::::'''Sunday:''' There is but one place that lingers in my thoughts, though.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the IPC...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115127-->
::::::'''Sunday:''' The shadow of Lady Bonajade still looms over me.
::::::'''Sunday:''' She shared some intriguing words with me before she left. She said that if I cannot find the answer I seek among the stars, the Strategic Investment Department... will be the last refuge for the lost.
::::::'''Sunday:''' Perhaps one day, someone will find me and ask me to pay the price of freedom. I am ready for that, and I will certainly not be a burden to any of you.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About Robin...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115131-->
::::::'''Sunday:''' You may find this confusing, but among my worries, she is not one of them.
::::::'''Sunday:''' She can take care of herself... I should have admitted that long ago.
::::::'''Sunday:''' All I want is to lead the way for her. It's not about sibling rivalry. There are unknown hardships ahead, and I wish to face them first.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About your outfit...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115135-->
::::::'''Sunday:''' I am a fugitive, after all, and I shouldn't draw attention. I changed out of the family head's outfit the moment I gained my freedom.
::::::'''Sunday:''' Even though I was about to start my penance, I wanted to keep it for its sentimental value, but I lost it in Penacony.
::::::'''Sunday:''' Perhaps this is some sort of sign.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Return}} I have another question...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503114008_16-->
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::;(<!--Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString)-->)
::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the destination...
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115140-->
:::::::'''Sunday:''' It's funny that I never imagined I would be traveling with the Nameless one day.
:::::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503114008_59-->
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503114008_59-->
:::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} Are you planning to join the trailblazing journey?
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115142-->
::::::::'''Sunday:''' You mean, will I disembark when we reach the destination? Absolutely, I want to explore more of the world for the sake of my ascetic journey.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' Even without the power of the Order, I will do my utmost to lend a hand if needed.
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} Any destinations you're interested in?
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115145-->
::::::::'''Sunday:''' I do have a few ideas in mind, but as a mere hitchhiker, it's not really my place to weigh in.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' Creating a paradise remains my lifelong ambition. When I obtained permission and accessed the data bank, I came across many references to this concept throughout the universe.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' They go by different names &mdash; Kingdom of Heaven, Pure Land, Blissful Realm... Hopefully, I can visit these places to see if they truly live up to their names.
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the Eternal Centurion...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115149-->
::::::::'''Sunday:''' Are you concerned that I won't be able to escape its wrath, no matter where I go? Rest assured, if that were truly a possibility, I wouldn't have made the request to board the Express.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' The Family may wish to eliminate me, but as long as I'm not rallying a sizable army, they wouldn't go so far as to involve the Eternal Centurion.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' Since its inception, it was never meant to be used against a single person.
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::::{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all for now.
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115154-->
:::::::'''Sunday:''' My best regards, as always.
:::::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
