:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About your outfit...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115135-->
::::::'''Sunday:''' I am a fugitive, after all, and I shouldn't draw attention. I changed out of the family head's outfit the moment I gained my freedom.
::::::'''Sunday:''' Even though I was about to start my penance, I wanted to keep it for its sentimental value, but I lost it in Penacony.
::::::'''Sunday:''' Perhaps this is some sort of sign.
:::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::{{DIcon|Return}} I have another question...
::::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503114008_16-->
::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} Life on the Express...
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115104-->
:::::::'''Sunday:''' Please ask away. But I might not have a lot to share since I've only recently came on board.
:::::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503114008_19-->
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503114008_19-->
:::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the companions on the Express...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115106-->
::::::::'''Sunday:''' I'm trying to connect with everyone using my new identity, but I may need some time due to my personality.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' Mr. Yang showed me the captivating way of the Trailblaze during our travels. Truth be told, you've all been great teachers.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' The conductor taught me about the history of the Nameless, Dan Heng showed me the extensive knowledge stored in the data bank, and even from Miss March 7th, I've learned...
::::::::'''Sunday:''' ...
::::::::'''Sunday:''' A lot.
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About your book...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115112-->
::::::::'''Sunday:''' It was a gift I received, and it arrived blank.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' Did you mistake it for some type of classic text or something? It's not entirely inaccurate, though. I wrote some pages myself.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' In a way, it symbolizes a chapter of my life.
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::::{{DIcon|Talk}} What have you been up to lately?
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503115116-->
::::::::'''Sunday:''' Most of the time, I've been reflecting in solitude while waiting for our departure.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' I wanted to contribute, but I wasn't sure how. The conductor just told me to wait patiently.
::::::::'''Sunday:''' Yet... as I look at the spacious car, I feel a strong urge to organize it that likely stems from boredom...
